 2017-03842017-04-13,  INAC,  ,  , 
ActIndian Act
SubjectTransfer of administration and control of lands ** Nanoose Indian Reserve ** British Columbia
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise of the power of the province of British Columbia to take lands in NANOOSE INDIAN RESERVE, in British Columbia, pursuant to subsection 35(1) of the Indian Act; (b) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of the required lands, pursuant to subsection 35(3) of the Indian Act.
